SECTION VI: HISTORICAL ANALOGUES & COMPARATIVE ASSESSMENT

The Bab el-Mandeb closure scenario has precedent in both the scale of disruption and the political-economic consequences — though 2026's 'double chokepoint' scenario is qualitatively without modern precedent.
